#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[k-dimensional smooth submanifold of cartesian space]

A _$k$-dimensional smooth submanifold of $RR^(n)$_ is a subset $M$ of $RR^n$ with the following properties.
For all $x in M$ there is an open neighbourhood $Uu$ with $x in Uu$ with a diffemorphism $phi : Uu -> Vv subset RR^n$, such that
$
  phi(M nn Uu) = (RR^(k) xx {0}^(n-k)) nn Vv.
$

We call $phi$ a chart.
